Text.string: Hey, hot stuff. Got a proposition for you, provided you're a little bit of an exhibitionist. You in?
You up for some fun?
Entrance is over here. Or wherever you like. See ya after the show, sugar.
Poor Trudy. She'll be missed.
Oh, Jenny, Jenny. I had high hopes for her.
Lena was quite a looker! Too bad.
And finally, if you'll hand over Moxxi's token.
While you do what you do best, I'll figure out a way to cut Killavolt's cord for good. See ya at the bar later.
Kill-a-volt, Kill-a-volt!
Kill-a-volt! Kill-a-volt!
Kill-a-volt! Kill-a-volt!
Kill-a-volt! Kill-a-volt!
Snag those tokens and yours truly gets to strokin'.
Welcome to “Who Wants to Bang a Bazillionaire”! The rules are simple. Each contestant has a token. Whoever gets four tokens first wins a single serving of yours truly.
Get in there and show old KV you want that electric D!
Let the bullets fly, my competitors! Win and nothing less than ecstasy will be your reward.
Ever heard of seven minutes in heaven? If you come out on top, that's what you get.||—B-but don't time me or anything.
Things are really starting to heat up! But save some juice for the after-party, eh?
You know you want it! I'm the superconductor of the boof train! Choo-choo!
The winner gets to show me their “ohm” face!
If you wanna get amped with Killavolt, get out there and con-DUIT!
The only thing better than the buzz you feel after a scrump with Killavolt is the buzz you feel DURING!
Fight hard enough and you get the SHOCKER!||—Yes, I know what it means. I'm rebranding it.
Ha! I never let him into my bar, for the record. He didn't satisfy my cravings, so... I often drank alone.
Don't feel too bad about taking out those other contestants. Anyone who'd compete to sleep with that man, well... they're a menace to society.
Take his backpack, Vault Hunter. I've got just the place for it at my bar.
That's the one.
You know, I might use this just for the pleasure.
Install it there, would ya, sugar?
Killavolt was always human trash. If you ask me, that's just where he belongs.
I'm talkin' SEX STUFF! Two rounds if I've got the juice.
All right, volt-heads! Let the games begin!
Quit it!
Ooh, not so rough!
You can play with my ball if you win.
Quit knockin' my big ball!
Stop it!
My, you're a naughty one.
Harder! Harder!
Oh, too hard!
Be gentle with my big ball, jeez!

When I dated Killavolt, he was just... Kenneth. The break up hit him hard. He started chugging battery acid to bulk up. I've got to find a way to dampen his charge... which gives me an idea. Bring Moxxi a few batteries, would ya?
Looks like Moxxi's crew are real bloodhounds! If you win, I might have to put a shock collar on you! Don't worry, I've got a matching pair. Rawrrrr.
Cold-blooded, calculating, and just a whiff of battery acid—Moxxi's crew is my type!
Moxxi's crew must really want those tokens! Easy, volt-heads. There's plenty of current to go around.
Hey Moxxi's crew. How about I put my positive with your negative and let's see if we can make the sparks fly?
Whoever wins the contest is gonna get some post-coital ice cream. Guess Killavolt's favorite flavor. Go on, guess. Shocky-road!
I love this show!

Good. If you didn't know, I host an interplanetary battle royale called the Underdome. But I'm not the only one. There's a celebrity bandit named Killavolt who's hosting a livestreamed fight to the death in Promethea's Seaport District. Killavolt's a total skeezeball and he's giving battle royale a bad name. So, we're gonna pull the plug on his show. I'll meet you down on the planet.
Looks like Moxxi's crew's going toe-to-toe with Trudy the Toeless of Pandora! Who's missing three toes but still fights like a psychopath? I'm looking at you, Trudy!
And Trudy is outta there! Looks like someone won't be getting a pre-coital foot rub! Best of luck next time, Trudy!
One down, two to go for Moxxi's crew. Can she go all the way?||—Yes. Yes, she can. Trust me.
I know he's gross, but pay it no mind, sugar. Eyes on the prize. Let him run his mouth now before we stick some soap in it.
We've got a new contestant, Jenny of Raden-3. Look out, Moxxi. She's got your number. By the way, I lost it, so if you survive, ring-a-ding-ding, baby!
And Jenny's out for the count! All this bloodshed over little old me—I'm starting to feel a spark, volt-heads!
Two down, one to go! I'm not surprised Moxxi's crew's coming out on top. That's her favorite position.
It's not, but I told him it was. Had to get mine somehow. His circuits are a little short, if you catch my drift.
Give it up for Lena, hailing all the way from the swamp planet of Eden-6. According to her entry form, she likes crushing Vault Thieves and squeezing grogs. How about that?!
And Moxxi's crew has sent the grog grabber from Eden-6 back into the mud. Too bad! I've got a jungle she could tame!||—Seriously, guys, has anyone seen my trimmer?

The grand prize winner of Killavolt's contest gets to sleep with the man himself. Now, there's plenty of reasons a woman might enter a battle royale to the death. Cash. Fame. A gun that can melt a man's face off. But bedding Killavolt? That's no prize. Trust me.
Oh my! We have ourselves a winner! Make your way to my casa, and we'll start an electrical fire!
It's showtime. Give Killavolt that token of my affection.
Before you go up against Killavolt, get me those batteries, would ya, sugar? I've got to find a way to use Killavolt's overcharged personality against him.
Killavolt's an electro-lightweight, if you ask me. He won't go anywhere without that electricity shield of his.
My nana used to say a man hides his weakness under his pride, and that gave me an idea. Just one more battery left.
That'll do just fine.
I found a way to shock Killavolt into submission.
Find me, and I'll tell you how we're gonna yank the cord on Killavolt.
Pop in those batteries, sugar.

Killavolt might not have stolen my heart, but he did steal my Underdome. I had plans for a battle royale on Promethea. This little contest makes a mockery outta the time-honored and incredibly arousing tradition of gladiatorial combat. But if I have anything to say about it, he's not gonna be the last man standing.
Oh, just a warning about Killavolt. Every word that man says makes me want to pull the trigger, if you catch my drift. And we will. Soon enough.
Tell Killavolt this is a token of my affection—right before you shoot him in the face. And anywhere else you feel he's so deserving, if you catch my drift.
Shoot him in the dick. That's the drift.
Hey, where's Moxxi? She's the lucky winner, not you. You're just some nothing Vault Thief.
My crew has the tokens. I'll be there soon, Kenneth.
It's Killavolt now! And whatever. You can watch, I guess. I'm feeling adventurous.
Nyghghghghghghgh!
You friggin' nerd.
Go shock yourself, Kenneth.
I am neither man, nor woman, but both deserve more respect than you give.
Consider your circuits fried.
I... just wanted to be loved...
All fizzle, no sizzle—as always, Kenneth. Good riddance!
Thanks for the help, sugar. Let's chat.
Full disclosure, we used to date. After I left, he joined the Children of the Vault. A cult of mindless followers must have been a magnet for an insecure nothing like Killavolt.

You sure know how to please a girl in front of an audience, sugar. I'm happy to call you my champion any time you like. Look, this ain't the most civilized galaxy, I get that. I can't shoot every sonofabitch who runs his mouth or tries to disrespect me, heh...||... but I can try.
Oh, please.
Ignore him, sugar.
Don't let Killavolt get under your skin, Vault Hunter.

If you didn't know, I host an interplanetary battle royale called the Underdome. But I'm not the only one. There's a celebrity bandit named Killavolt who's hosting a livestreamed fight to the death. Killavolt's a total skeezeball and he's giving battle royale a bad name. So, we're gonna pull the plug on his show.
Whoa! My wires are tingling! I'm not supposed to play favorites, but I feel electricity in the air!
When you go head-to-head against Killavolt, I want to make sure you have some protection.
Best battle royale ever!
Get to dying, Vault Thief!
Hope you're ready to get chopped, Vault Thief!
Moxxi! I was hoping you'd show up. You entering to win the grand prize? Ehhh?
Killavolt! Pick me next!
We love you, Killavolt!
You'll never make it out of this alive, Vault Thief!
(oohs, laughter, cheers)
(oohs, laughter, cheers)
(oohs, laughter, cheers)
(oohs, laughter, cheers)
Hey, Moxxi's crew! I hope you're as freaky in the sheets as you are deadly in the streets!
Ooh, I like the way you work that trigger finger. Maybe I'll let you flip my favorite switch with it.
Ohhh, you're really going for it, huh? All these contestants just DYING to meet me. I love it!
I can't take my eyes off you, contestant. You're like poetry in motion, if poetry was super deadly.
He's clearly compensating for something, and I know exactly what that something is.
Ugh. What a pig.
You know it. I've brought a champion to fight in my name. Besides, I wanna draw it out. Let my circuits charge a little bit before we connect.
Just focus on the mission, sugar.
He'll get his eventually. Just not the way he thinks.
Ohhh! And Moxxi's crew is REALLY cleaning up out there!
Oh-hoh-hoh! Folks, did you see that kill?
What a show! Moxxi's crew really knows how to make a guy feel special.
Check out Moxxi's crew, making a splatter painting! Nasty!
Splat! They're really making a mess!
Whoa! That was ugly!
Hey, hey! Very nice!
Moxxi's crew is doing some good work out there!
Wooo! Killavolt's the man!
That's what I like to see!
Moxxi's crew is on the hunt for one of our contestants! Looks like we've got a deathmatch on our hands!
It's time for another showdown! These contestants are fighting to the death for my affections! It's a beautiful thing!
Our contestants are getting ready for a fight! Get those tokens, folks, so you can meet the man, the legend... me, Killavolt!
What have we here? A new contestant!
What an entrance! The fight for my affection is heating up!
We've got a new contestant, Jenny of Raden-3. Woah, looks like somebody let her out of her cage! This should be good!
Our new contestant's got a zipline straight to my heart!
If you're just tuning in, this is “Who Wants to Bang a Bazillionaire”, where four contestants fight to the death to win one night with me, Killavolt!
Remember, folks: whichever contestant gets all four tokens wins a steamy night with yours truly!
Welcome back to “Who Wants to Bang a Bazillionaire”, where four lucky contestants fight battle royale style for my affections!
We've got a great lineup of contestants today, including a Vault Thief fighting for the sexalicious Miss Moxxi.
Welcome to all our new viewers! You've tuned into “Who Wants to Bang a Bazillionaire”, hosted by me, Killavolt! I'm also the grand prize!
Hey, what the hell is Moxxi's crew doing? Get back to the battle royale!
This isn't part of the game! Get back in there and fight!
Where the hell is Moxxi's crew going? They're off the map!
Hey! HEY! That area's off limits! Where are you going?! That's Moxxi and I's love nest! I swear!
Hand me those batteries, sugar.
In my spare time, I like to make my own toys. This one, it's a... modification, something I cooked up in the bedroom.
This little device should help us short out Killavolt's defenses when you hand in my token. I think he'll find it rather shocking.
